# Huginn Suite — Implementation Tasks

## Phase 1: Unified Data Model
- [ ] Design shared JSON schema (`huginnVersion`, `tasks`, `projects`, `milestones`, `dependencies`, `calendarEvents`, `timekeeping`)
- [ ] Create `experimental/huginn_data.js` — schema, validation, normalization, versioning, import/export helpers
- [ ] Create `experimental/muninn_test_fixture.json` — reference test data with edge cases
- [ ] Migrate Tasks v7.4 to use shared data module
- [ ] Migrate Cal v1.0 to use shared data module
- [ ] Migrate Timekeeper v0.1 to use shared data module
- [ ] Verify roundtrip: export from one component → import in another

## Phase 4: Huginn Plan (New Component)
- [ ] Project hierarchy tree data structures and CRUD
- [ ] Auto-creation of start/end milestones and default task on project creation
- [ ] Tree view UI with expand/collapse, layer filtering, full-text search
- [ ] Inline editing with edit mode and hotkeys
- [ ] Task↔Project conversions (breakdown, group, flatten)
- [ ] Dependency management between tasks/milestones
- [ ] Scheduler: critical path, conflict detection, constraint types (flexible/fixed/target)
- [ ] Gantt chart view synchronized with tree view
- [ ] Dependency arrows and critical path highlighting in Gantt
- [ ] "Personal tasks" L1 auto-project from Huginn Tasks
- [ ] CSV export of current view

